{"tid":435010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因強風關係 青嶼幹線及汀九橋實施臨時交通措施　青嶼幹線擠塞","createTime":"2017-10-14T00:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T01:12:56.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57f8692a81d01a8481c56cf84aab906adbbdde44","tid":435010,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"運輸署宣布，由於強風關係，青嶼幹線及汀九橋實施臨時交通措施。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，措施包括青嶼幹線中線封閉，容易被風吹倒的車輛須改行下層等。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，現時上址交通擠塞，呼籲須行經有關路段及前往機場人士，預留充裕時間及考慮使用非路面交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n另外，汀九橋亦因為強風，中線暫時封閉。"},{"pid":"8603418ba14b02eda229071a17b29bf53f329938","tid":435010,"uid":41868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"想問點解係封中線 唔係應該封慢線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20928f8ab323f06336b7aa6d04247cf71e062713","tid":435010,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問點解係封中線 唔係應該封慢線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n架車左搖右擺 封中線唔驚大風時左右車太近搞到撞"},{"pid":"07fc7e30061ac77a7b04f57c2c95b60f5e301579","tid":435010,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T01:02:52.000Z","msg":"哇塞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6614fa4baaddd9d3b606fa1e34e8d1e70aeae73","tid":435010,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"機場飛機照起飛？"},{"pid":"544b7eb8d158989f7ccf30b4407adb3004c2b0ec","tid":435010,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T01:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機場飛機照起飛？</blockquote><br />\n仆街係欣澳點渣走"}]}